    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 X、谷歌尚未申请马来西亚新社交媒体许可证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/musk-s-x-google-yet-to-apply-for-malaysia-s-new-social-media-license</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据马来西亚互联网监管机构称，埃隆马斯克的 X 和运营视频流媒体平台 YouTube 的 Alphabet Inc. 的谷歌尚未根据马来西亚周三生效的新法律申请社交媒体运营许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/musk-s-x-google-yet-to-apply-for-malaysia-s-new-social-media-license</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 00:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
